description:
A collection of eight stories, "Cyberabad Days" is a triumphant return to the India of 2047 (the India of 
River of Gods
); a new, muscular superpower in an age of artificial intelligences, climate-change induced drought, strange new genders, and genetically improved children.contents:9 • America is Not the Only Planet (2009) essay by Paul McAuley13 • Sanjeev and Robotwallah (2007) short story31 • Kyle Meets the River (2006) novelette51 • The Dust Assassin (2008) novelette79 • An Eligible Boy (2008) novelette109 • The Little Goddess (2005) novella155 • The Djinn's Wife (2006) novelette199 • Vishnu at the Cat Circus (2009) novella
